Rating: 4
Amazing! As everyone said moist on the inside, crispy on the outside. Best thing about it is the way the savory just gives the chicken so much flavor. I did it with the deglazing sauce and recommend that too.

Rating: 3
I did turn the chicken on its sides while roasting and enjoyed the way that method browned the lower parts of the bird nicely - Visually very appetizing. Chicken was very moist and flavorful... I stuffed the cavity of the bird as well, using the same ingredients mixed with bread crumbs, and made a gravy out of the glaze for a more traditional meal, with great results. Only problem - smokes heavily - was afraid my fire alarm would go off!

